'''麥可·皮內達'''（{{lang-es|Michael Francisco Pineda Paulino}}，{{bd|1989年|1月18日}}）出生於[[多明尼加共和國|多明尼加共和國]]的[[聖克里斯多堡省|聖克里斯多堡省]]，為[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]的[[先發投手|先發投手]]，目前效力於底特律老虎。皮內達於2005年以自由球員身份和[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]簽約，然後在2011年首次升上大聯盟。在新人球季第一年，他就入選參加[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]，在[[美國職棒大聯盟年度最佳新人獎|美聯最佳新人獎]]獲得第5名。

==小聯盟時期==
2005年12月12日，皮內達在16歲的年紀和[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]簽下合約<ref name=tradecentral>{{cite web |last=Manuel |first=John |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/majors/trade-central/2012/2612811.html |title=Majors: Trade Central: Yankees Use Montero To Acquire Pineda From Mariners |publisher=BaseballAmerica.com |date=January 13, 2012 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2017-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725141518/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/majors/trade-central/2012/2612811.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年他參加多明尼加夏季聯盟（Dominican Summer League），開始了他的棒球職業生涯，繳出2勝1敗、0.44防禦率的成績。2007年他繳出6勝1敗、2.29防禦率的成績。2008年，皮內達在水手1A的威斯康辛木紋響尾蛇（Wisconsin Timber Rattlers）開始他的球季，繳出8勝6敗、1.95防禦率的成績，被打擊率只有0.216，並且投出128次三振。美國棒球雜誌將他評為水手農場裡面最有前景的第10名<ref>{{cite web|last=Eddy|first=Matt|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2009/267278.html|title=Seattle Mariners top 2009 prospects|publisher=Baseballamerica.com|date=December 5, 2008|accessdate=January 17, 2012|archive-date=2011-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214143133/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2009/267278.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外他還被評為小聯盟裡最佳的投手<ref>{{cite news |first=John |last=Hicke |url=http://www.seattlepi.com/sports/article/M-s-finish-first-wave-of-skipper-interviews-1291520.php |title=M's finish first wave of skipper interviews |publisher=seattlepi.com |date=November 13, 2008 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2018-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629234241/https://www.seattlepi.com/sports/article/M-s-finish-first-wave-of-skipper-interviews-1291520.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年，皮內達因為受傷的關係，錯了整個球季<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120113&content_id=26345470&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy|first=Lyle|last=Spencer|title=Gutsy deal is worth risk for Mariners, Yankees|publisher=[[Major_League_Baseball_Advanced_Media|Major League Baseball Advanced Media]]|date=September 24, 2011|accessdate=January 14, 2012|archive-date=2012-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120128154343/http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120113&content_id=26345470&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，美國棒球雜誌將他評為水手農場裡面最有前景的第7名<ref name=ba2010>{{cite web |last=Eddy |first=Matt |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2010/269393.html |title=Seattle Mariners top 2010 prospects |publisher=Baseballamerica.com |date=January 22, 2010 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2017-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426144417/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2010/269393.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這一年他在2A繳出了8勝1敗、2.22防禦率的成績，62.1局裡面投出76次三振和17個保送<ref>{{cite news |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2012750838_its_official_michael_pineda_sh.html |title=Mariners Blog | It's official: Michael Pineda shut down for rest of year, has "great chance" to make 2011 club, Zduriencik says |newspaper=[[Seattle_Times|Seattle Times]] |date=August 28, 2010 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2010-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008031750/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2012750838_its_official_michael_pineda_sh.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外他還獲得了美國棒球雜誌跟[[今日美國|今日美國]]日報評為小聯盟裡面最佳投手和最佳球員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2012930093_texas_rangers_at_mariners_sept.html |title=Mariners Blog | Texas Rangers at Mariners: Sept. 17, 2010 game thread |newspaper=Seattle Times |date=September 17, 2010 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2010-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100920033944/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2012930093_texas_rangers_at_mariners_sept.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=tradepr/>。

2011年，美國棒球雜誌將皮內達評為水手農場潛力新秀裡面第2名<ref>{{cite web |last=Glassey |first=Conor |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2011/2611021.html |title=Seattle Mariners top 2011 prospects |publisher=Baseballamerica.com |date=December 6, 2010 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2012-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120116232022/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2011/2611021.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是職業棒球裡面最好的球員第7名<ref name=ba2011>{{cite web |url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2011/2611328.html |title=Prospects: Rankings: Top 100 Prospects: 2011 Top 100 Prospects |publisher=BaseballAmerica.com |date=February 23, 2011 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2011-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226135537/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/top-100-prospects/2011/2611328.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


==大聯盟時期==
===西雅圖水手===
[[File:Michael_Pineda_on_May_10,_2011_(2).jpg|right]]的皮內達。]]
2011年球季，[[西雅圖水手|西雅圖水手]]將皮內達升上大聯盟，並且成為5名先發輪值投手中的第5號先發，也是第3位在開幕戰就成為先發投手的年輕球員（其他2名球員是Chris Sale和Tim Collins）<ref name=tradepr/>。4月5日是他在大聯盟的第一場先發比賽，於客場對[[德州遊騎兵|德州遊騎兵]]，投6局失3分，最後吞下敗投<ref>{{cite news|url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2014693962_mariners_pleased_with_michael.html|date=April 5, 2011|title=Mariners pleased with Michael Pineda debut|first=Geoff|last=Baker|newspaper=Seattle Times|accessdate=February 11, 2012|archive-date=2011-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814180949/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2014693962_mariners_pleased_with_michael.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月12日對[[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]的比賽，他投7.1局失2分，最後球隊以3：2獲勝，他也順利拿下大聯盟生涯的第1勝<ref>{{cite news|url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/mariners/2014756766_mari13.html|title=Michael Pineda dazzles as Mariners win second straight, 3-2: Rookie pitcher Michael Pineda turned to his trusted heat, striking out seven as the Mariners beat the visiting Blue Jays 3-2 despite an eighth-inning scare|first=Geoff|last=Baker|newspaper=Seattle Times|date=April 12, 2011|accessdate=February 11, 2012|archive-date=2011-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831045027/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/mariners/2014756766_mari13.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月28日的比賽中，他於6局的投球中投出生涯新高的9次三振<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2011/04/video_tigers_offensive_struggl.html|title=Video: Tigers' offensive struggles continue against Seattle Mariners rookie phenom Michael Pineda|date=April 28, 2011|first=James|last=Schmehl|work=MLive.com|accessdate=February 11, 2012|archive-date=2011-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711110220/http://www.mlive.com/tigers/index.ssf/2011/04/video_tigers_offensive_struggl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。皮內達在大聯盟第一個月的表現為4勝1敗、防禦率2.01的成績，並於31.1局投出30次的三振，如此優異的表現讓他獲得了美國聯盟單月表現最佳投手獎項<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110503&content_id=18575660&vkey=pr_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |title=Michael Pineda of the Seattle Mariners voted winner of the Gillette Presents American League Rookie of the Month Award for April | MLB.com: Official Info |publisher=Mlb.mlb.com |date=May 3, 2011 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110132939/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/press_releases/press_release.jsp?ymd=20110503&content_id=18575660&vkey=pr_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月10日，皮內達獲選參加生涯第一次的[[2011年美國職棒大聯盟全明星賽|全明星賽]]，他接替[[賈斯丁·韋蘭德|賈斯丁·韋蘭德]]投球，他完美的三振了[[史考特·羅倫|史考特·羅倫]]和Rickie Weeks <ref>{{cite news |author=Times |url=http://www.spokesman.com/stories/2011/jul/11/ms-pineda-chosen-to-replace-verlander-on-all-star/ |title=M’s Pineda chosen to replace Verlander on All-Star team – Spokesman.com – July 11, 2011 |publisher=Spokesman.com |date=July 11, 2011 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2015-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022122107/http://www.spokesman.com/stories/2011/jul/11/ms-pineda-chosen-to-replace-verlander-on-all-star/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於明星賽前皮內達的成績113局的投球中繳出為8勝6敗、3.03防禦率、113次三振和36次保送的成績<ref>{{cite news|last=Christopher |first=Ryan |url=http://sports.yahoo.com/mlb/news?slug=ycn-8795055 |title=Michael Pineda shines for Seattle Mariners in All-Star game: A fan's reaction – MLB – Yahoo! Sports |publisher=Sports.yahoo.com |date=July 13, 2011 |accessdate=January 14, 2012}}</ref>。2011年球季，皮內達的成績171局的投球中繳出為9勝10敗、3.74防禦率、173次三振和55次保送的成績<ref>{{cite news |url=http://espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/story/_/id/7460297/new-york-yankees-deal-jesus-montero-seattle-mariners-michael-pineda-source-says |title=New York Yankees deal Jesus Montero for Seattle Mariners' Michael Pineda, source says – ESPN New York |publisher=Espn.go.com |date=January 13, 2012 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306131049/http://espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/story/_/id/7460297/new-york-yankees-deal-jesus-montero-seattle-mariners-michael-pineda-source-says |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在球季最後兩個月的7場先發裡面，他沒有拿下任何勝投<ref name=trade>{{cite news |url=http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120113&content_id=26344064&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy |title=Mariners, Yanks nearing Michael Pineda, Jesus Montero swap | yankees.com: News |publisher=Newyork.yankees.mlb.com |date=January 13, 2012 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2012-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120128131900/http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120113&content_id=26344064&vkey=news_nyy&c_id=nyy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在今年的[[美國職棒大聯盟年度最佳新人獎|美聯最佳新人獎]]獲得第5名的成績（前4名排名依序為[[傑瑞米·海利克森|Jeremy Hellickson]]、[[馬克·川柏|Mark Trumbo]]、Eric Hosmer和[[伊萬·諾瓦|Ivan Nova]]）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2016766395_michael_pineda_fifth_dustin_ac.html |first=Geoff |last=Baker |title=Mariners Blog | Michael Pineda fifth, Dustin Ackley sixth in AL Rookie of the Year voting | Seattle Times Newspaper |publisher=Seattletimes.nwsource.com |date=November 14, 2011 |accessdate=January 14, 2012 |archive-date=2012-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229033243/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/marinersblog/2016766395_michael_pineda_fifth_dustin_ac.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===紐約洋基===
2012年1月，[[紐約洋基|紐約洋基]]以[[赫蘇斯·蒙特羅|Jesús Montero]]與Héctor Noesí和水手交易皮內達與José Campos<ref name=trade/><ref name=tradepr>{{cite press release|url=http://newyork.yankees.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120123&content_id=26440572&vkey=pr_nyy&c_id=nyy|title=Yankees acquire RHP Michael Pineda in four-player trade|publisher=Major League Baseball Advanced Media |date=January 23, 2012 |accessdate=January 23, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120116&content_id=26360652&vkey=affililiate&c_id=sea|title=Pitching depth allowed Mariners to deal Pineda: Prospects Walker, Paxton a big part of club's future plans|first=Greg|last=Johns|work=MLB.com|publisher=MLB Advanced Media|date=January 16, 2012|accessdate=January 17, 2012}}</ref>。

2012年球季，由於皮內達春訓尾聲時傳出肩膀不適的消息，最被放進傷兵名單中<ref>{{cite news |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120330&content_id=27764054&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |title=Yankees right-hander Michael Pineda to begin year on DL with shoulder tendinitis |work=MLB.com |publisher=Major League Baseball Advanced Media |first1=Bryan |last1=Hoch |first2=Paul |last2=Hagen |date=March 31, 2012 |accessdate=March 31, 2012 |archive-date=2012-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502170551/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120330&content_id=27764054&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月25日，球隊宣布，皮內達的肩關節唇有撕裂傷，將在5月2日動手術，預計需要1年的時間休息與復健，也宣告本季將不會出賽。[[布萊恩·凱許曼|布萊恩·凱許曼]]今天表示：「我大受打擊，投手永遠有風險，但這是我冬天所做的重要交易，要補進投手總是要張大眼睛。一開始就遇到這種事，相當讓人難受，但顯然對球員自己來說更難受。皮內達是個好孩子，他很認真訓練。我們最不希望看到的，也是他最不希望看到的就是手術，但考量到所有的狀況，這是目前最好的做法」。他相信水手事前也不知道皮內達的傷勢狀況，也強調交易時皮內達接受過完整的體檢。他說：「我們有機會做完整的體檢，我們也做了，結果沒問題。皮內達過去沒有過肩膀的問題，他也沒有向水手抱怨過，水手也不曾對他的肩膀做過任何檢查。這只是一個隨時都可能發生的不幸事件，而最後真的發生了」。總教練[[喬·吉拉迪|喬·吉拉迪]]說：「這是個損失，我們今年本來很期待他」，「這很不幸，但我們何時、何處、如何做了什麼事情都不重要，我們現在要做的是繼續前進，試著讓他恢復健康」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/story/_/id/7855551/new-york-yankees-michael-pineda-2012-shoulder-injury|title=Michael Pineda out for 2012"|date=April 25, 2012|accessdate=April 25, 2012|first=Wallace|last=Matthews|publisher=ESPN|work=ESPN New York|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426113308/http://espn.go.com/new-york/mlb/story/_/id/7855551/new-york-yankees-michael-pineda-2012-shoulder-injury|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


==球探報告==
皮內達是身高6尺7吋體重260磅的選手<ref name=trade/>。2011年他的快速球球速平均為94.7 mph，為大聯盟史上投超過100局的新人裡球速最快的<ref name=tradecentral/>，在現役球員裡面排名第4名，其他3名是Alexi Ogando、[[賈斯丁·韋蘭德|賈斯丁·韋蘭德]]和[[大衛·普萊斯|大衛·普萊斯]]。另外美國棒球雜誌提到皮內達在水手農場系統裡，他有很好的快速球<ref name=ba2010/>。皮內達除了有很好的快速球，他還能投出優異的滑球解決打者<ref name=ba2011/>，另外還能投出變速球<ref>{{cite news|url=http://espn.go.com/blog/new-york/yankees/post/_/id/26241/pineda-is-not-a-finished-product|title=Pineda is "not a finished product"|date=January 17, 2012|accessdate=January 17, 2012|first=Andrew|last=Marchand|publisher=ESPN|work=ESPN New York|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306040504/http://espn.go.com/blog/new-york/yankees/post/_/id/26241/pineda-is-not-a-finished-product|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


